WEBVTT

00:10.611 --> 00:12.136
Wow.

00:13.688 --> 00:15.422
You guys all look how I feel.

00:17.391 --> 00:20.493
Happens when your worst day
is immortalized in print.

00:20.528 --> 00:21.761
Bad karma.

00:21.796 --> 00:23.396
Bad karma for what?

00:23.431 --> 00:25.398
We were all just staring
to groove, weren't we?

00:25.433 --> 00:27.067
I should have never doubted myself.

00:28.870 --> 00:30.837
I should have gotten there sooner.

00:30.872 --> 00:33.506
My personal life affected
my decision-making.

00:33.541 --> 00:35.675
Guys, I should have made
a diagnosis sooner.

00:35.710 --> 00:37.777
But we can't just sit here
beating ourselves up over it.

00:37.812 --> 00:39.398
- Okay?
- I feel like we can.

00:40.615 --> 00:41.681
Or at least I can.

